{"tid":652902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★港珠澳大橋地盤垃圾袋藏男腐屍　無ID無明顯致命傷","createTime":"2018-05-04T08:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T13:46:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6b8996c3036c87099f2edb008b4b882515b72d0c","tid":652902,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:23:06.000Z","msg":"東涌暢連路近東岸路港珠澳大橋一個工地。早上10時18分，警方接獲工人報案，指在上址發現一個黑色膠袋，內裏藏有異物感到可疑。警方到場調查，發現膠袋打結，遂剪開膠袋，露出一具背部有紋身的男屍，屍身已腐爛，於是將封鎖範圍擴大至100米，架起帳篷遮蓋屍體，鑑證科人員已到場搜證，正追查死者的身分及死因，新界南總區重案組探員已接手調查。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，涉事港珠澳大橋工地位於大橋旁邊，現正進行路面擴建工程，放有一列水馬，該處對開種有不少樹木，對面為旅遊巴士停泊區。現場消息稱，早前曾有泥頭車在工地卸泥，藏有屍體的黑色膠袋懷疑連同泥頭一同卸下，直至今早始揭發事件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180504/bkn-20180504120802860-0504_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180504%2Fbkn-20180504120802860-0504_00822_001.html&d=0Kqj9glGY8Ts%2FbhUAvMUJkbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=5b74ce05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180504/bkn-20180504120802860-0504_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"d33dd24e1e6a1e6fb626e931a32646f1105a2088","tid":652902,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:23:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7837ee0067fd4786c00d55d47b2e9193d18032f5","tid":652902,"uid":92611,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:24:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"390ceb9afed748f13a7e62f76495b07d930a2eb6","tid":652902,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:24:35.000Z","msg":"港珠澳大橋工地位於大橋旁邊<br />\n<br />\n好明顯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77bfe410a2f3815745f611034a5d2a1911edd80","tid":652902,"uid":73340,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:24:42.000Z","msg":"泥頭車裝屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f8bb8d5c9fbcffef95ef2cff1390e2f5089599","tid":652902,"uid":17738,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:25:09.000Z","msg":"危險爺爺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42419cea2fe6660fd6c3013c87aa6c6ca0eb04d8","tid":652902,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:26:36.000Z","msg":"唔夠樁"},{"pid":"94b01ae9b026e5f274f765bb0573d3f45a35715e","tid":652902,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3128d05e33fdd278ad7e047f06477272f0cce02","tid":652902,"uid":16676,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:47:59.000Z","msg":"將來大把<br />\n<br />\n條天橋行經機場南, 但又未過香港關<br />\n<br />\n大陸/澳門出關無乜會搜車<br />\n<br />\n係天橋掉d 野落橋底 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n搵人接應執垃圾咋嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到時點止垃圾, 毒品都唔奇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458aa4dcebb8669587ac69d24960e1c584d81add","tid":652902,"uid":19552,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"血祭大橋"},{"pid":"3e41ec489e0f4b9409df8dd9e0082ac8e6b4d301","tid":652902,"uid":25635,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:49:11.000Z","msg":"打生樁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80e97aae99cbe26da6d2689bbea1ee1b5a74b75","tid":652902,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:50:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.geocities.jp/kyoketu/kazurahasi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.geocities.jp%2Fkyoketu%2Fkazurahasi.jpg&h=17d5025c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85ae363c0dbd088bcda73bc135c7b65c04ec4314","tid":652902,"uid":19552,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:51:01.000Z","msg":"打生樁，是東亞民間在建築前的習俗，日本稱之為「人柱」。從現今的角度去看，這個習俗既恐怖又駭人，它是在建築工程動工前，把一兩名兒童活埋生葬在工地內，其目的是祈禱工程順利。相傳這個方法是由魯班首度提出的，當人們在一處地方動土時，便會破壞該處風水，且會觸怒該處的冤魂，以致在建造期間時常發生意外，因此便出現了「打生樁」，把小孩生葬在工地上用作鎮邪，以減少出現的意外。"},{"pid":"9da09d8de93b9fbe31c44bab0ed56fbe4be6bca1","tid":652902,"uid":90601,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:51:55.000Z","msg":"條友知道得太多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05127a16fadb852d03e2e6660feca314860f94e6","tid":652902,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:52:19.000Z","msg":"打生樁要童男童女喎......"},{"pid":"eba20e842cfc2537ae2ed9837c52af48fdc7babf","tid":652902,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:55:24.000Z","msg":"鳩鐵個地盤埋左幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"066ee10fbb2656e2bd0102895d257625b5495fe3","tid":652902,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/165843_e0e355c30dd7895a8871ad8ffa989910.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F165843_e0e355c30dd7895a8871ad8ffa989910.png&h=0afed028&s={SIZE}\" 